text:
A long time ago. 
I'd appreciate its central conceit (even) more now than I did then.
S a c k  p e o p l e .
"Everyone is an ethnonationalist for people they like" is basic common sense. Only weird leftists pretend not to understand it.
... Anything else is saying you want them to cease to exist, which sound strange and sinister -- even to Europeans -- when directed at anybody other than Europeans.
